<q-input v-model="inputVal" outlined hint="說明" label="姓名" class="is_require"> </q-input>
<q-input v-model="text" outlined hint="說明" placeholder="請輸入手機號碼" label="Outlined" />
<q-input v-model="text" clearable outlined hint="clearable" placeholder="請輸入手機號碼" label="Outlined" />
<q-input v-model="text" outlined hint="Disable" disable />
<q-input v-model="text" outlined hint="Readonly" readonly />
<q-input v-model="text" outlined hint="Disable and readonly" disable readonly />
<q-input v-model="text" outlined placeholder="Placeholder" />
<q-input v-model="text1" outlined class="is_require" label="姓名" :rules="[(val) => !!val]" />

<q-input
  v-model="text"
  outlined
  placeholder="請輸入10碼"
  error-message="請輸入10碼"
  :rules="[(val) => val.length === 10]"
/>

<q-input
  v-model="text"
  outlined
  label="Phone"
  mask="(###) ### - ####"
  unmasked-value
  hint="Mask: (###) ### - ####"
/>

<q-input
  v-model="text"
  outlined
  label="Phone"
  mask="(###) ### - ####"
  fill-mask
  unmasked-value
  hint="Phone"
/>

<q-input
  v-model="cardNo"
  outlined
  label="Card"
  mask="#### - #### - #### - ####"
  fill-mask="#"
  hint="Mask: #### - #### - #### - ####, FillMask: #"
/>

<q-input v-model="password" outlined :type="isPwd ? 'password' : 'text'" hint="Password with toggle">
  <template v-slot:append>
    <q-icon
      :name="isPwd ? 'visibility_off' : 'visibility'"
      class="cursor-pointer"
      @click="isPwd = !isPwd"
    />
  </template>
</q-input>

<q-input v-model="text" outlined hint="說明" :dark="darkMode" label="Outlined" placeholder="Placeholder">
<template v-slot:append>
  <q-icon name="search" color="primary" />
</template>
</q-input>

<q-input
  v-model="text"
  outlined
  hint="說明"
:dark="darkMode"
label="Outlined"
color="secondary"
placeholder="Placeholder"
>
<template v-slot:append>
  <q-icon name="search" color="secondary" />
</template>
</q-input>

<q-input
  v-model="text"
  outlined
  label="Outlined"
:dark="darkMode"
color="positive"
placeholder="Placeholder"
>
<template v-slot:append>
  <q-icon name="search" color="positive" />
</template>
</q-input>

<q-input v-model="text" outlined label="Outlined" :dark="darkMode" placeholder="Placeholder">
<template v-slot:prepend>
  <q-icon name="event" color="primary" />
</template>
</q-input>

<q-input
  v-model="text"
  outlined
  label="Outlined"
:dark="darkMode"
color="secondary"
placeholder="Placeholder"
>
<template v-slot:prepend>
  <q-icon name="event" color="secondary" />
</template>
</q-input>

<q-input
  v-model="text"
  outlined
  label="Outlined"
:dark="darkMode"
color="positive"
placeholder="Placeholder"
>
<template v-slot:prepend>
  <q-icon name="event" color="positive" />
</template>
</q-input>
<q-input v-model="time" outlined type="time" hint="Native time" />
<q-input v-model="date" outlined type="date" hint="Native date" />
<q-input v-model="number" outlined type="number" hint="number" />

<q-input
  outlined
  type="file"
  hint="Native file"
@update:model-value="
  (val) => {
    file = val[0];
  }
"
/>

<q-input
  multiple
  outlined
  type="file"
  hint="Native file (multiple)"
@update:model-value="
  (val) => {
    files = val;
  }
"
/>

<q-file v-model="model" outlined bottom-slots label="Label" counter max-files="12">
<template v-slot:before>
  <q-icon name="folder_open" />
</template>
<template v-slot:hint> Field hint </template>
<template v-slot:append>
  <q-btn round dense flat icon="add" @click.stop.prevent />
</template>
</q-file>
